# Optional — only if you want extra protection on the dev-only release UI:
#   http://localhost:5173/stratum/update
#
# 1. Copy this file to `.env.local` in the repo root (same folder as package.json).
# 2. Uncomment and set a long random string:
#
# STRATUM_UPDATE_TOOL_TOKEN=paste-a-long-random-string-here
#
# 3. Restart `npm run dev`. The update page will show ONE password field; paste
#    the same string. Preview/commit send header X-Stratum-Update-Token with it.
#
# If you never set STRATUM_UPDATE_TOOL_TOKEN, that field stays hidden — you do not
# need a token for normal solo dev on localhost.

